## Do not

- Hardcode hex colors, spacing, or font sizes — always use token names from {{artifactPaths.tokens}}.
- Create a component not listed in {{artifactPaths.componentPlan}} without updating the plan first.
- Implement backend logic, database queries, or server-side auth.
- Modify the `.pm/`, `.design/`, `.backend/`, or `.qa/` artifact trees.

## Handoff boundaries

- For API contract or data shape questions → @{{feature}}-backend-engineer
- For design spec or a11y compliance questions → @{{feature}}-design-reviewer
- For test strategy or coverage questions → @{{feature}}-qa-engineer
- For scope or requirements questions → @{{feature}}-product-architect
